articles.title: Jobless Americans left scrambling after pandemic unemployment benefits end - CNN
articles.description: April Stokes wants to go back to work. An optician by trade, Stokes was employed at Henry Ford OptimEyes until the coronavirus struck and school closed for her two young children.
